title: Nancy Kerrigan's Friend on Tragedy
description: Todd Eldredge, friend and former teammate of Olympic ice skater Nancy Kerrigan, spoke to Maggie Rodriguez about the death of Kerrigan's father and the reported psychological evaluation of her brother.
